  "time_ut": 1656139790,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b95\u0ba3\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0bc2\u0bb2\u0bae\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0b87\u0bb1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0baf \u0b85\u0ba9\u0bc1\u0bae\u0ba4\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Permission to import goods through open account",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Permission has been granted to import 10 essential commodities including rice, sugar and pulses through open account.",
        "The permission for this will be given from July 01, said the Minister of Commerce.",
        "An open account is a system in which payments are made to distributors after the goods have been imported.",
        "It is noteworthy that the importation of goods under this bank account system has been carried out before. (R)"
      ],
